&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2087&quot;&gt;If you are motivated by impact, growth, and purpose, you will find a strong sense of belonging at Quince.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;2290&quot; data-local-id=&quot;6a0d0d38-3057-4834-9012-12f09f19e465&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;fabric-text-color-mark&quot; data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot; data-text-custom-color=&quot;#0747a6&quot;&gt;&lt;u data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;THE ROLE

